798
00:56:27,519 --> 00:56:30,659
[SPEAKER_02] Totalno mi je to onaki takav.

799
00:56:30,659 --> 00:56:31,820
[SPEAKER_02] To je baš dio mene.

800
00:56:31,820 --> 00:56:37,860
